name: The Qubist Wave
description: "The Qubist Wave" is a reappropriation of "Houses and Tree" by Georges Braque as he invented Cubism at the port of L’Estaque in 1908. At the same period, Quantum Mechanics and General Relativity were slowly emerging. Nowadays, physics has begun its reunification with the digital world: “It From Bit”. The universe is seen as a soapy foam, an ocean of information waves, whose constituent atoms, pixels of space-time, organize themselves in a network...
